<h3>Generator Options</h3>

<ul>
  <li><code>--directory</code>: Customize the component location (defaults to <code>app/views/rui/components</code>)</li>
  <li><code>--stimulus</code>: Include Stimulus controller named <code>pagination_controller.js</code></li>
</ul>

<h3>Component Properties</h3>

<h4>Navigation Configuration</h4>
<ul>
  <li><code>prev_url</code>: URL for the "Previous" link (String, optional - disabled if nil)</li>
  <li><code>next_url</code>: URL for the "Next" link (String, optional - disabled if nil)</li>
  <li><code>classes</code>: Additional Tailwind classes for the navigation wrapper (String, optional, defaults to "text-slate-500 sm:text-sm text-base font-medium dark:text-slate-300")</li>
</ul>

<h4>Page Items Configuration</h4>
<ul>
  <li><code>pages</code>: Array of page items (Array, required). Supports three formats:
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Integer:</strong> Inactive page number that renders as a clickable link</li>
      <li><strong>String:</strong> Active/current page number with highlighted styling</li>
      <li><strong>Symbol :gap:</strong> Renders an ellipsis (&hellip;) for page gaps</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

<h4>Styling Configuration</h4>
<ul>
  <li><code>active_classes</code>: Custom CSS classes for active page styling (String, optional, defaults to "<code>py-2 px-4 block border-t-2 border-primary-500 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 dark:border-primary-400 dark:hover:bg-primary-500/30</code>")</li>
</ul>

